### **3) Metric Alignment (Measure the Right Outcomes)**

**What to add/change in Power BI**

* Replace single “velocity focus” with **Balanced Scorecard**
* Combine AI + Delivery in one view

**KPIs (balanced)**

* **Output**: Velocity, Stories Delivered
* **Efficiency**: Cycle Time, PR Merge Time
* **Quality**: Defect Density, PR Rework/Comments
* **AI Impact**: Acceptance Rate, LOC Accepted, Rework Reduction

**New composite**

* **Effective Delivery Index (EDI)**
  = Velocity × (1 − Defect Rate) × (1 − Rework %)

**Targets**

* EDI ↑ consistently even if raw velocity fluctuates

**AI enablement**

* True “AI ROI” explanation (quality vs speed trade-off)
* Identify teams where AI is helping vs hurting

